{"tid":968309,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[多謝張超雄] 南亞男女反轉港鐵車廂 食煙推撞踢幕門","createTime":"2019-01-04T06:43:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-04T08:49:51.000Z","uid":12609,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"4a510e722e156ab61ff607f03b52d5b2903e7b5f","tid":968309,"uid":12609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T06:43:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190103/large/1546518555_463d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190103%2Flarge%2F1546518555_463d.jpg&h=c998c049&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190103/59102286\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190103%2F59102286&d=JS6%2Bb5RV8sKIbXK7uPI%2FUKS6uTmBE%2FuUnOR61Sj848o%3D&h=c29b5d60\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190103%2F59102286&h=59040b7f\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190103/59102286</a><br />\n<br />\n一班南亞裔男女喺中環夜蒲之後散band，唔知係玩到未回魂，定係漠視規例，竟然喺港鐵車廂食煙、推撞，仲要踢幕門，唔係覺得自己咁樣好型吓嘛？讀者Thomas噚日(2日)朝早6點幾，喺蘭桂坊通宵夜蒲後搭港鐵去旺角，佢同嗰班南亞裔男女一齊上車，目擊晒佢哋惡行。<br />\n<br />\n其中3個男嘅坐喺Thomas對面，中間着住黑色西裝外套、黑boots、手戴粗金鏈好似「大佬」咁款嗰位，竟然喺車廂食煙，其間支煙跌咗落地，佢非常慳家咁執返起！鏡頭一轉，嗰班男女突然同另一班南亞裔男女嘈起上嚟，兩班人你推我撞，車廂入面嘅乘客急急腳避開，雖然聽唔明佢哋嘈乜，但聽語氣都知好重火藥味。<br />\n<br />\n呢個時候，列車去到油麻地站，已經廣播please stand back from the train door，準備閂車門，煲煙男一幫五人急急轉身落車，其中染橙色頭髮嘅同伴仲回頭向對方手指指，同行金毛女伴用力拉住車門，令車門彈返開，橙髮男仲一腳踢開月台幕門，等「大佬」可以落車。<br />\n<br />\n橙髮男跟住「大佬」行出月台，當佢哋以為用咗最有型嘅方法離場嗰陣，其餘兩男一女同伴就落唔切車，車門又閂咗，金毛女邊拍車門邊爆粗，橙髮男又試夾硬拉開車門，金毛女都唔弱幫手齊齊令到車門再打開，終於齊齊落車。未到站嘅Thomas聽返仲喺車廂嘅另一幫男女講，兩班人本來唔識嘅，但前一晚夜蒲嗰陣佢哋曾經嘈過交，點知喺港鐵狹路相逢，有人撩交嗌。<br />\n<br />\n港鐵就話冇呢件事嘅記錄，亦冇收到乘客報告，唔清楚實際清況。但都提醒乘客港鐵範圍嚴禁吸煙，車站當眼位置已經貼咗不准吸煙告示。如果乘客見到有人喺鐵路範圍食煙或行為影響到其他人，可通知職員採取適切行動。"},{"pid":"f465129cca23d2863e7e5fb1ab6b5dbde836d65b","tid":968309,"uid":21545,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T06:45:58.000Z","msg":"死南亞mk <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1daf5388fb660cdaa4580e15fe7f1c5bf5941000","tid":968309,"uid":107364,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T06:49:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2b7337309b2e83a14d33a3c7ed3cfa36f828921f","tid":968309,"uid":90660,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T06:57:19.000Z","msg":"張超雄不得好死"},{"pid":"19a0904bc682bfb908fa7fabc3e940c42ced0933","tid":968309,"uid":162533,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T07:01:17.000Z","msg":"我識啲南亞人好nice"},{"pid":"d52643c31deafbd4dfb6b95745302835d604bb66","tid":968309,"uid":31200,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T07:02:22.000Z","msg":"唔知點解諗起佢落唔切車要拉開度門個畫面好好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d8aa9a813990e17cb34d636880175ac262b1b69","tid":968309,"uid":11719,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T07:03:45.000Z","msg":"社會毒瘤"},{"pid":"f502fdf81b496de4da2320c0577ddfa01eb198ce","tid":968309,"uid":190928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T08:39:03.000Z","msg":"垃圾"},{"pid":"e21227d9e5935a3d3156cf170fbf8928508bf5c4","tid":968309,"uid":161341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T08:47:49.000Z","msg":"張狗仲話要大愛唔好歧視<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n人地班蝻殺人放火 樣樣做齊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"332496bb470ebdac04d0d43589772145b8d9b51a","tid":968309,"uid":67500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T08:48:27.000Z","msg":"SD俾張超雄"},{"pid":"43ada53711328140bd785bf47a7392bec02cc6a9","tid":968309,"uid":58630,"like":0,